{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Alcohol. Action. Violence. Get ready to take your friends &quot;behind the sauna&quot;.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finnish Cabin Mayhem aims to provide an old school arcade shooter experience with a focus on chaotic melee combat. Use whatever there is at hand as a weapon to clubber your enemies in numerous different levels and game modes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Alcohol infused multiplayer madness </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy various alcoholic beverages and beat the opposition with complex martial art techniques. Loot and utilize various improvised weapons such as sausages, baseball bats and pellet guns.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/cabinMayhemGIF1.gif?t=1731917377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>High-octane action in multiple environments</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drive bikes, plant mines, go to sauna and fire disposable rocket launchers. Gain access to ancient mythical weapons hidden in the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/BikeFight.gif?t=1731917377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Zombie mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle for your life against an endless horde of zombies in a co-op zombie mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/SuomiKPZombies.gif?t=1731917377\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Character customization</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose your character and unlock stylish apparel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135990/extras/cabinMayhemC